instant feedback soon after

3
00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:07.010
or even while a user is interacting with the web browser

4
00:00:07.010 --> 00:00:09.010
can be considered a real-time app.

5
00:00:09.010 --> 00:00:10.070
Think of how chat apps,

6
00:00:10.070 --> 00:00:12.000
they give a visual cue

7
00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:14.000
to indicate that a chat message recipient

8
00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:16.050
is currently typing a response.

9
00:00:16.050 --> 00:00:19.090
Creating apps like these could be useful for many reasons.

10
