In this video, we'll talk about some popular reasons

11
00:00:22.050 --> 00:00:25.000
why you would want to learn to create a real-time app

12
00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:27.010
using the Spring framework.

13
00:00:27.010 --> 00:00:29.030
I like to call this my top five reasons why

14
00:00:29.030 --> 00:00:33.020
